{"tid":1658632,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"遊行口號都要升級    香港人  報仇！","createTime":"2019-10-16T14:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T03:34:02.000Z","uid":8873,"like":11,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3de9f7857a635c484c9bbee6eacb2eb1b4f459c1","tid":1658632,"uid":8873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:22:06.000Z","msg":"發展到第四個月對家已經殺人滅口毀屍滅跡 非常惡毒嘅對爭取自由嘅香港人<br />\n<br />\n港共政權無數次迫害真心為香港付出嘅人<br />\n美國方面應該會通過制裁官員。證明係可以反咬佢哋<br />\n我哋香港人亦都要比對家知道我哋有仇必報。10倍奉還<br />\n<br />\n我哋嘅口號亦都要升級由加油反抗。演變城更有力嘅報仇<br />\n<br />\n為左咁多個月付出鮮血生命手足。報仇！"},{"pid":"540c35caaba425db4755a4f2296b5cc902a7e383","tid":1658632,"uid":8873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a262c590333854cc5d61e0491a2b021e38d6bf5f","tid":1658632,"uid":8873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:24:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/byH1rCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbyH1rCM.jpg&h=7ddc61b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"297005a3fcac04db4335740c600ef48f2783f2c1","tid":1658632,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:24:27.000Z","msg":"以牙還牙 十倍奉還"},{"pid":"ece7928c83fabf91ad8e00c85c9baa8c5b487080","tid":1658632,"uid":8873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"297005a3fcac04db4335740c600ef48f2783f2c1","tid":1658632,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:24:27.000Z","msg":"以牙還牙 十倍奉還"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:25:41.000Z","msg":"冇理由淨係我哋俾人打冇得覆桌"},{"pid":"8ffee3decb82bdf0294171c3661b06a9e61d698c","tid":1658632,"uid":8873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad8f8eae98a0acba481